title: Eyðvør Klakstein
text:
Eyðvør Klakstein (born 5 September 1995) is a <a href="Faroe%20Islands">Faroese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> midfielder who currently plays for <a href="K%C3%8D%20Klaksv%C3%ADk%20%28women%29">KÍ</a>. From August 2015 until May 2016 she was playing for <a href="CD%20Marino">CD Marino</a> in the second best football division in <a href="Spain">Spain</a>.
